        (cast(
            sum(case 
                when p.hospitaldischargetime is not null 
                     and date(p.hospitaldischargetime, '+2 years') > '2105-12-31 23:59:00' 
                     and p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' then 1 
                else 0 
            end) as float) 
        / count(distinct p.patientunitstayid)), 4
    ) as two_year_survival_probability
from 
    patient p
join 
    diagnosis d 
on 
    p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
where 
    d.diagnosisname = 'wound infection - surgical wound'
    and p.hospitaldischargetime is not null;

input: calculate the two year survival probability of patients who were prescribed atorvastatin calcium 80 mg po tabs after having been diagnosed with
predict:
WITH diagnosed_patients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT d.patientunitstayid
    FROM diagnosis d
    JOIN medication m ON d.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
    WHERE LOWER(d.diagnosisname) = 'metabolic alkalosis'
      AND LOWER(m.drugname) = 'atorvastatin calcium'
      AND LOWER(m.dosage) = '80 mg'
      AND LOWER(m.routeadmin) = 'po tabs'
),
two_year_survival AS (
    SELECT p.patientunitstayid,
           p.hospitaldischargetime,
           p.hospitaldischargestatus,
           julianday('2105-12-31 23:59:00') - julianday(p.hospitaldischargetime) AS days_since_discharge
    FROM patient p
    WHERE p.patientunitstayid IN (SELECT patientunitstayid FROM diagnosed_patients)
),
survival_stats AS (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(CASE WHEN hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' AND days_since_discharge <= 730 THEN 1 END) AS survived_730_days,
        COUNT(patientunitstayid) AS total_patients
    FROM two_year_survival
)
SELECT 
    CAST(survived_730_days AS FLOAT) / CAST(total_patients AS FLOAT) AS two_year_survival_probability
FROM survival_stats;

input: what is the minimum total cost of a hospital, including a procedure called bronchodilator - leukotriene
predict:
SELECT MIN(total_cost) AS min_total_cost
FROM (
    SELECT c.hospitalid, SUM(c.cost) AS total_cost
    FROM cost c
    JOIN treatment t ON c.eventid = t.treatmentid AND c.eventtype = 'treatment'
    JOIN patient p ON c.patienthealthsystemstayid = p.patienthealthsystemstayid
    WHERE t.treatmentname = 'bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonists'
    GROUP BY c.hospitalid
) subquery;
real: select min(t1.c1) from ( select sum(cost.cost) as c1 from cost where cost.patienthealthsystemstayid in ( select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid from patient where patient.patientunitstayid in ( select treatment.patientunitstayid from treatment where treatment.treatmentname = 'bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonists' ) ) group by cost.patienthealthsystemstayid ) as t1;

input: since 3 years ago, how many patients were diagnosed with sepsis - sepsis with single organ dysfunction- metabolic encephalopathy during the same month after the diagnosis with sepsis - sepsis with single organ dysfunction- acute
predict:
WITH sepsis_diagnosis AS (
    SELECT 
        d1.patientunitstayid, 
        d1.diagnosistime AS sepsis_time
    FROM 
        diagnosis d1
    WHERE 
        d1.diagnosisname = 'sepsis - sepsis with single organ dysfunction- acute respiratory failure'
        AND d1.diagnosistime >= DATE('2105-12-31', '-3 years')
),
encephalopathy_diagnosis AS (
    SELECT 
        d2.patientunitstayid, 
        d2.diagnosistime AS encephalopathy_time
    FROM 
        diagnosis d2
    WHERE 
        d2.diagnosisname = 'sepsis - sepsis with single organ dysfunction- metabolic encephalopathy'
),
filtered_patients AS (
    SELECT 
        s.patientunitstayid
    FROM 
        sepsis_diagnosis s
    JOIN 
        encephalopathy_diagnosis e
    ON 
        s.patientunitstayid = e.patientunitstayid
        AND STRFTIME('%Y-%m', e.encephalopathy_time) = STRFTIME('%Y-%m', s.sepsis_time)
)
SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT patientunitstayid) AS patient_count
FROM 
    filtered_patients;
